					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1708" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1025&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1366&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你家的貓咪也會感情好到一起上廁所嗎？日本一位飼主近日分享自家貓咪的有趣行為引起 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/26/%e4%b8%8a%e5%bb%81%e6%89%80%e4%b9%9f%e8%a6%81%e4%b8%80%e8%b5%b7%ef%bc%9f%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%a7%8a%e5%a6%b9%e6%b7%a1%e5%ae%9a%e7%9c%8b%e8%91%97%e5%bd%bc%e6%ad%a4%e5%81%9a%e8%9b%8b%e7%b3%95%e8%ae%93/">上廁所也要一起？貓咪姊妹淡定看著彼此做蛋糕讓主人笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1708" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1025&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1366&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/neakasa-rS98UQ_zCoU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你家的貓咪也會感情好到一起上廁所嗎？日本一位飼主近日分享自家貓咪的有趣行為引起網上熱議，她發現某天家中兩隻愛貓不約而同，分別在面對面的貓砂盆內上廁所，並嚴肅地對視彼此，仿佛在進行無聲的對決，讓她當場看了笑翻。&nbsp;</p>



<p>原來這名飼主在家裡養了兩隻貓咪，她經常會在社群平台上分享與紀錄愛貓的日常點滴，日前她發文透露，為了避免貓咪搶用廁所，提升如廁舒適度，家中已經按照網友們的建議設置了多個貓砂盆，沒想到卻意外出現了搞笑畫面。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1220" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=1220%2C1220&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-217671" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?w=2338&amp;ssl=1 2338w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=1536%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=2048%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lynda-b-WsEti0PVe3s-unsplash.jpg?resize=146%2C146&amp;ssl=1 146w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">飼主某天發現自家養的兩隻貓咪，竟不約而同地一起到貓砂盤上做蛋糕<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>這天家裡的兩隻貓咪不約而同地分別蹲坐在左右兩側的貓砂盆，牠們彼此互相凝視，臉上寫滿嚴肅與專注，雖然沒有發出聲音，也沒有肢體動作，但兩貓仿佛在進行隔砂盆的無聲式交鋒，感覺隨時會開打的逗趣模樣令人忍俊不禁。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這場搞笑又有趣的對峙大戲迅速引發熱議，許多貓奴與鏟屎官看完感到共鳴，紛紛在底下留言表示「一對活寶」、「感情也太好」、「像極了相撲開場」、「難道是做蛋糕大賽」、「好好笑」、「要是我家的貓可能直接開扁」、「貓界名場面」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/26/%e4%b8%8a%e5%bb%81%e6%89%80%e4%b9%9f%e8%a6%81%e4%b8%80%e8%b5%b7%ef%bc%9f%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%a7%8a%e5%a6%b9%e6%b7%a1%e5%ae%9a%e7%9c%8b%e8%91%97%e5%bd%bc%e6%ad%a4%e5%81%9a%e8%9b%8b%e7%b3%95%e8%ae%93/">上廁所也要一起？貓咪姊妹淡定看著彼此做蛋糕讓主人笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
